    <span class="badge"><span class="badge-icon" aria-hidden="true">ðŸšš</span><span>Fast free shipping</span></span>
  </div>
  <div class="container footer-bottom">
    <p class="footer-credit"><a class="nav-link" href="https://alaayounsi.vercel.app/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Website created by Alaa Younsi</a></p>
